_sText:
Made for [FnG]'s gungame server.

Intended for: Deathmatch/GunGame
~15 spawns per team
Completely indoors, no skybox needed

--V1.0--
Added Fog
Fixed you being able to see the other players when you spawn by adding walls
Added more cover boxes
Made it easier to get on the middle platform
Textured the map to no longer be dev textures
